    "",
    "Sarah approved closing the investigation. The debugging engineer will be reassigned to AI Copilot improvement starting Sprint 25.",
    "",
    "## New Discussion Items",
    "",
    "### 1. December MRR Projection (15 minutes)",
    "",
    "Sarah shared the latest revenue numbers. November MRR closed at $1,549,040 (Basic: $97,299, Pro: $241,423, Enterprise: $1,210,318). December is tracking to $2,273,427 based on confirmed renewals and new deals in the pipeline.",
    "",
    "The December breakdown by tier:",
    "- Basic: $144,305 (6.3% of total) — 168 accounts",
    "- Pro: $476,427 (21.0%) — 178 accounts",
    "- Enterprise: $1,652,695 (72.7%) — 154 accounts",
    "- Total: $2,273,427",
    "",
    "Sarah highlighted the concentration risk: Enterprise alone is $1,652,695, which is 72.7% of total MRR. If even 5 Enterprise accounts churn in January, we could lose approximately $50K MRR (assuming average Enterprise MRR of $10,732 per account). This concentration is both our strength (high ARPU) and our vulnerability.",
