    "",
    "Jake raised the technical requirement for EU data residency. Currently all data is stored in US-East (AWS us-east-1). For GDPR compliance and to satisfy EU Enterprise requirements, we need a European data region. He proposed AWS eu-west-1 (Ireland) with an estimated 8-week implementation timeline in Q2 2026.",
    "",
    "Action item: Li Wei to start localization audit for German and French UIs. Scope: translate all user-facing strings, date formats, number formats, and legal text. Estimated effort: 4-6 weeks with a translation partner.",
